          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2018-10-23T15:33:42Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Modernizing Disclosures for Investors Act </b></p> <p>This bill directs the Securities and Exchange Commission to: (1) report on the costs and benefits of requiring reporting companies to use Form 10-Q to satisfy quarterly financial disclosure requirements; and (2) make recommendations for decreasing costs, increasing transparency, and increasing efficiency of quarterly financial reporting by emerging growth companies. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-10-11T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
